    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，描述 setupTestDetector 的完整决策逻辑。核心是从 shouldSuggestSetup() 开始，判断要不要给用户弹出测试配置的建议。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是 shouldSuggestSetup()。那第一步要判断什么？是不是要先看看之前有没有处理过类似的确认？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，先检查「Is a confirmed/rejected confirmation?」。如果是已经确认或拒绝过的，就直接走到 No suggest or run confirmed command 的分支，不再重复打扰用户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "ConfirmSuggest"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画上了 C 节点，用虚线连到 A，然后 Yes 分支指向 ConfirmSuggest。那如果答案是 No 呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "No 的话进入 D 节点，判断「/setupTest 是否被禁用，或者有没有带任何测试的 controller」。这两个条件只要满足一个，就不建议了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "NoSuggest"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以 D 的 Yes 分支直接到 No Suggestion，这是一个终止节点。那 D 为 No 的情况呢？",
